## Stack
GitHub Copilot agent mode in VS Code is the primary harness. Per-harness config lives in `.vscode/settings.json` (terminal auto-approve list), `.github/instructions/` (scoped instructions applied automatically by file pattern), and `.github/prompts/` (reusable slash-command prompts). For capability details, check [code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot](https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot) — always current. PowerShell default shell (CI may run PS 5.1; local is PS 7).

